stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> BuildInput
  BuildInput --> ModelEvent: call model
  ModelEvent --> Final: no tool intent
  ModelEvent --> ParseIntent: tool_use
  ParseIntent --> PolicyCheck: valid schema
  ParseIntent --> Recover: invalid schema
  PolicyCheck --> ToolExecution: allowed
  PolicyCheck --> UserApproval: needs approval
  PolicyCheck --> Recover: denied
  UserApproval --> ToolExecution: approved
  UserApproval --> Recover: rejected
  ToolExecution --> Observation: result / error
  Observation --> StateUpdate
  StateUpdate --> BuildInput: next turn
  Final --> [*]
  Recover --> StateUpdate
